Laura Innes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laura_Innes 0 Laura Elizabeth Innes (born August 16, 1957) is an American actress and television director. She played Dr. Kerry Weaver on the NBC medical drama ER, and Sophia on the NBC thriller The Event. Laura_Elizabeth_Innes ( born August_16_,_1957 ) is an_American_actress_and_television_director .
